%C3%A2n-h%E1%BB%AFu/poem-maRxAMOCboIbSdvxXl781Q">Phong tật chu trung phục chẩm thư hoài tam thập lục vận, phụng trình Hồ Nam thân hữu - 風疾舟中伏枕書懷三十六韻，奉呈湖南親友</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Ph%E1%BB%A5ng-H%C3%A1n-Trung-v%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-th%E1%BB%A7-tr%C3%A1t/poem-th4wiD8xku-UZhGlQVc-Dg">Phụng Hán Trung vương thủ trát - 奉漢中王手札</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-H%C3%BAc/S%C6%A1n-th%C3%B4n-khi%E1%BB%83n-ho%C3%A0i/poem-qk2VsGhuocApaZN_AMyBcw">Sơn thôn khiển hoài - 山村遣懷</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-H%C3%BAc/author-udskGfyCijQjK6PP08MOjw">Nguyễn Húc</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Th%C3%B4ng-m%C3%A3-h%C3%A0nh/poem-d3d4bfpW8cqvFGANyYEv4g">Thông mã hành - 驄馬行</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br></div>	</div>
